def get_glove(name, dim):
    with open(path+ 'glove.' + name + '.txt', 'r') as f: lines = [line.split() for line in f]
    print(len(lines))
    words = [d[0] for d in lines if len(d) == dim + 1]
    vecs = np.stack(np.array(d[1:], dtype=np.float32) for d in lines if len(d) == dim + 1 )
    wordidx = {o:i for i,o in enumerate(words)}
    save_array(res_path+name+'.dat', vecs)
    pickle.dump(words, open(res_path+name+'_words.pkl','wb'))
    pickle.dump(wordidx, open(res_path+name+'_idx.pkl','wb'))

def create_emb():
    n_fact = vecs.shape[1]
    emb = np.zeros((vocab_size, n_fact))

    for i in range(1,len(emb)):
        word = idx2word[i]
        if wordidx.get(word) is not None and re.match(r"^[a-zA-Z0-9\-]*$", word):
            src_idx = wordidx.get(word)
            emb[i] = vecs[src_idx]
        else:
            # If we can't find the word in glove, randomly initialize
            emb[i] = normal(scale=0.6, size=(n_fact,))

    # This is our "rare word" id - we want to randomly initialize
    emb[-1] = normal(scale=0.6, size=(n_fact,))
    emb/=3
    return emb

idx = imdb.get_word_index()

path = get_file('imdb_full.pkl',
                origin='https://s3.amazonaws.com/text-datasets/imdb_full.pkl',

f = open(path, 'rb')
(x_train, labels_train), (x_test, labels_test) = pickle.load(f)

vocab_size = 60000

trn = [np.array([i if i<vocab_size-1 else vocab_size-1 for i in s]) for s in x_train]
test = [np.array([i if i<vocab_size-1 else vocab_size-1 for i in s]) for s in x_test]

lens = np.array(list(map(len, trn)))

def res_block(input_layer, units ):
        dense_layer_1 = Dense(units, activation='linear')(input_layer)
        dense_activation_1 = PReLU()(dense_layer_1)

        dense_layer_2 = Dense(units, activation='linear')(dense_activation_1)
        dense_activation_2 = PReLU()(dense_layer_2)

        resnet_layer = Add()([dense_activation_1, dense_activation_2])
        return resnet_layer

def create_model(model_type):
    
    emb = create_emb()

        ##define the input data source, create embedding for non-numerical data
    main_input = Input(shape=(seq_len,), dtype='int32', name='main_input') # each data source can be added as a seperate input source
    main_embedding = Embedding(vocab_size, WV_DIM, input_length=seq_len, weights=[emb], trainable=False)(main_input)
    main_embedding_dropout = SpatialDropout1D(0.2)(main_embedding)
    
    if model_type == 'dilation_cnn_attention':



        conv_out = conv1d_block(main_embedding)
        conv_pooling, score = Attention(return_attention = True)(conv_out)
        #conv_pooling = Attention()(conv_out)


        resnet_layer_1 = res_block(conv_pooling, D_DENSE)
        resnet_dropout_1 = Dropout(0.5)(resnet_layer_1)
        
        resnet_layer_2 = res_block(resnet_layer_1, D_DENSE)
        resnet_dropout_2 = Dropout(0.5)(resnet_layer_2)
        
        dense_layer_out = Dense(1, activation='sigmoid')(resnet_dropout_2)
        
        model_task = Model(inputs=main_input, outputs= dense_layer_out)
        model_attention = Model(inputs=main_input, outputs=score )


        return model_task, model_attention
        
    elif model_type == 'bi-lstm-attention':
        
 
        lstm_layer_1 =Bidirectional(LSTM(D_LSTM, return_sequences=True, kernel_initializer='Orthogonal'))(main_embedding_dropout)

        lstm_pooling, score = Attention(return_attention = True)(lstm_layer_1)

        resnet_layer_1 = res_block(conv_pooling, D_DENSE)
        resnet_dropout_1 = Dropout(0.5)(resnet_layer_1)
        
        resnet_layer_2 = res_block(resnet_layer_1, D_DENSE)
        resnet_dropout_2 = Dropout(0.5)(resnet_layer_2)
        
        dense_layer_out = Dense(1, activation='sigmoid')(resnet_dropout_2)
        
        model_task = Model(inputs=main_input, outputs= dense_layer_out)
        model_attention = Model(inputs=main_input, outputs=score )


        return model_task, model_attention
        
    elif model_type == 'cnn-bi-lstm-attention':
        
        conv_out = conv1d_block(main_embedding)

        lstm_layer_1 =Bidirectional(LSTM(128, return_sequences=True, kernel_initializer='Orthogonal'))(conv_out)

        lstm_pooling, score = Attention(return_attention = True)(lstm_layer_1)

        resnet_layer_1 = res_block(conv_pooling, D_DENSE)
        resnet_dropout_1 = Dropout(0.5)(resnet_layer_1)
        
        resnet_layer_2 = res_block(resnet_layer_1, D_DENSE)
        resnet_dropout_2 = Dropout(0.5)(resnet_layer_2)
        
        dense_layer_out = Dense(1, activation='sigmoid')(resnet_dropout_2)
        
        model_task = Model(inputs=main_input, outputs= dense_layer_out)
        model_attention = Model(inputs=main_input, outputs=score )


        return model_task, model_attention
        
    else:
  

        conv_out = conv1d_block(main_embedding)

        conv_pooling, score = Attention(return_attention = True)(conv_out)

        resnet_layer_1 = res_block(conv_pooling, D_DENSE)
        resnet_dropout_1 = Dropout(0.5)(resnet_layer_1)
        
        resnet_layer_2 = res_block(resnet_layer_1, D_DENSE)
        resnet_dropout_2 = Dropout(0.5)(resnet_layer_2)

        model_task = Model(inputs=main_input, outputs= dense_layer_out)
